snippet.title: Game & Watch - Mario Bros. (c)1983 Nintendo [MAME emulation footage]
snippet.description:
This the Game & Watch Mario Bros, a Multi Screen series Game & Watch unit from Nintendo from 1983.  This was one of the more commonly seen units back in the day.

Work on the emulation of this unit was done by hap, and Sean Riddle.  DarthMarino provided the artwork for more recently emulated units, while hydef was generally responsible for the artwork on ones emulated before 2020, links to the artwork are below

https://drive.google.com/drive/u/1/folders/1vl9O-0jIGCHHY_lrWpOwBtqTXEKsVGOY  DarthMarino 
https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1WLKcvynl0ky2mRL1UacA9yaiMTnNs4x5 hydef
